data.text:
Putnam, October 1989. Oversized Hardcover. Used - Very Good / No Jacket As Issued. Item #252040

ISBN: 0399134875

Two volume clothbound set in red slipcase. Slipcase cover photo is scratched; else, near fine condition. This is the trade edition, not the signed, limited edition but it is SIGNED BY JOE DIMAGGIO on page 10 of the first volume, at the end of his introduction to the set. Includes a certificate of authentication by the previous owner, who had Joltin' Joe hand sign it for him at a card show in 1993.

Used Book
